title: Fruit Tycoon - Novel Updates
tags: Business Management   Game Elements   Level System   Male Protagonist   Modern Day
author: 二蛇
description:
The reality of society was now so, such that even if the woman may have even been the one pursuing at first, at the moment when she hears that there are as many as nine siblings in her to-be-partner's family, with the eldest brother also being the breadwinner of the family, she would without the least hesitation bid goodbye.

A story of an ordinary guy being granted a fruit app that would change his life forever.>
